Template::Plugin::PerlTidy - version 0.01

This modules is a Template Toolkit Filter for Perl::Tidy. It can be used
to automatically display coloured and formatted perl code in web pages.

Note that Perl::Tidy isn't available from the CPAN and must be downloaded 
its SourceForge page: http://perltidy.sourceforge.net

Author: Briac Pilpré <briac@cpan.org>
Copyright: This module is distributed under the same terms as perl itself.

